  "detailed_description": "Squarelands is sandbox adventure game where you explore a randomly generated world while fighting, building and becoming stronger as you play! Mainly inspired by Terraria, Squarelands aims to provide plenty of freedom for the player.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Day/Night Cycles<br></li><li>Mining, Crafting and Building<br></li><li>Procedural Map Generation<br></li><li>Fishing and Farming<br></li><li>Hundreds of Items and Objects<br></li><li>Death Penalties (and Optional Permadeath)<br></li><li>Key Rebinding</li></ul>",
